Array having fixed size , we can't increase the size as well we can't decrease , if array size is 5 maximum image store 5 elements we want store 6th element we have to create one more array with 
the extra space , but we can't increase the size.
But in array list the size will be dynamic , you can increase the size aswellas decrease .

