Greddy Algorithm:-

Custom sorting:-
If it sorting we have only two possiblities either ascending or desending , when it comes to custom sortin we can sort the value s according to our format.

Ascending order - 19,26,37.
Desencing order - 37,26,19. 

Custom sorting - 26,37,19 (unit wise) .

- From given arrays make pairs  
- sort the array based on nth type.

After for sure we will take first meeting , compare nth time to starting time of next pair , if staring time strictly greater , consider the meeting .


